LINKING TO WEBSITE- but to a specific page
<a href="(url with out http://www...)" target="_blank"></a>


LINKING TO AN ELEMENT ON YOUR PAGE-set a link using id and a attribute.


<a href="(define the id: #Hi)" alt="">item that is link</a>

<p id="Hi"> 
this paragraph will be the website that
the previous link will go to...basically, it will just scroll down. 
</p>

